---
---
  <section id="chi-sono" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Immagine -->
      <div class="fade relative">
        <div class="bg-cream-dark rounded-3xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5] relative">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=600&q=80" alt="Stefano Moretti"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
          <!-- Badge disponibile -->
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg px-4 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green rounded-full pulse"></span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800">Disponibile ora</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">· Empolese Valdelsa</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Decorazione -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-20 h-20 bg-orange-light rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-light rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Testo -->
      <div class="fade d1">
        <div
          class="inline-block bg-blue-light text-blue text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">
          Chi sono</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-5">
          Un consulente locale,<br>non un call center.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-light">Mi chiamo <strong
            class="text-gray-800 font-semibold">Stefano Moretti</strong>. Sono un agente di commercio specializzato in
          utenze energetiche, operativo nell'<strong class="text-gray-800 font-semibold">Empolese Valdelsa</strong> e in
          tutta la Toscana.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-light">Il mio approccio è semplice: ti spiego con parole
          chiare cosa stai pagando e ti aiuto a pagare meno — senza forzarti verso nessuna scelta. <strong
            class="text-gray-800 font-semibold">La decisione è sempre tua.</strong></p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">A differenza degli operatori telefonici, <strong
            class="text-gray-800 font-semibold">sono una persona fisica</strong>. Possiamo incontrarci di persona,
          chiamarci o scriverci. E sono disponibile anche dopo la firma.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">🏠 Privati</span>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">🏢 Aziende</span>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">🏪 PMI & Negozi</span>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">⚡ Luce</span>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">🔥 Gas</span>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">📍 Toscana</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
